race.comment: Over to the girls now and ANGELS FURY (6) is a filly by Harry Angel on debut for the Maher yard who debuts. She looked very sharp winning a recent jump out by a big space and looks to have plenty of ability. No surprise to see support for her, she can stake her Blue Diamond claim. STREISAND (1) has just found one better in both runs to date, edged out by Eurocanto on debut who we'll get a guide to in the race earlier. She's got speed and can give a sight here. LA GITANA (11) is a filly by Home Affaird on debut for the Hayes yard who has won a jumpout and was a $400,000 purchase. Watch the market. GHANA'S AKAN (3) was well backed on debut and ran a solid race with improvement to come.
